  "content": "<p data-pid=\"tJlZ_i3s\">我最感兴趣的是成年人的阅读理解，尤其是难懂的解释文本。一些笔记：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"qp4grc2v\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z59PYkSdPeznr95fco4GRQx\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">人们经常难以回忆起文本的细节，原因在于他们起初就根本没有加工文本</a><sup data-text=\"人们经常难以回忆起文本的细节，原因在于他们起初就根本没有加工文本\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/677786105\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup><br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"D2k0YU3_\"> （见 2023-06-30, 2023-08-01, 2023-08-31 patron letters）<br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"FUibGy02\"> 干预措施<br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"-O3_xas6\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zSoTbuyrXFnDHibaSeEzPRx\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">附加问题</a><sup data-text=\"附加问题\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/677785901\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"YdtKuBEK\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zLZUS7KTrG4ABm3tRLGxMMj\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">阅读理解问题可以发现文本基础的漏洞</a><sup data-text=\"阅读理解问题可以发现文本基础的漏洞\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678612702\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"3\">[3]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"H4pUZfy_\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zVKwVczp4nEAKPWqfS1BqMi\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">阅读理解问题令人不快</a><sup data-text=\"阅读理解问题令人不快\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678195187\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"4\">[4]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"Fx_4RLmP\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zAkgXnwHwuvrTjaFM49S5P1\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">教材的习题集并不善于检测阅读理解问题</a><sup data-text=\"教材的习题集并不善于检测阅读理解问题\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678405361\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"5\">[5]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"Pto8qW-M\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z4m9Gat7zi9YUmZzQRR7pwt\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">附加问题能够提高学习者对相关但未直接测试的内容的理解</a><sup data-text=\"附加问题能够提高学习者对相关但未直接测试的内容的理解\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/677786021\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"6\">[6]</sup><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"agMUS7Wp\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z5aepnaCuu6XiPqB4LgBDkH\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">助记媒介可能会促使读者更缓慢、更专注地阅读</a><sup data-text=\"助记媒介可能会促使读者更缓慢、更专心地阅读\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/478084993\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"7\">[7]</sup><br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"9mmTjLUP\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zCQYRYZTQRmrR4bFGCzCMkR\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">自我解释</a><sup data-text=\"自我解释\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678998358\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"8\">[8]</sup><br/> </li><ul><li data-pid=\"j1hTlXHI\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zUR6RM21Sa88cFDfC47svVv\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">精细口头复述</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"bcHK8r1I\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zVXYW2pJPC8iY8JhCCRKbMp\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">iSTART</a><br/> </li><li data-pid=\"zeFw3cXC\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/z7FLRWQNjaUQSvRQJYiqNQm\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">McNamara, D. (2004). SERT: Self-explanation reading training. Discourse Processes, 38(1), 1–30</a><br/> </li></ul><li data-pid=\"Uq1LEsWk\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zSv7fL6SRMchq1bvuoQjrxz\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">编写卡片有助于阅读理解</a><sup data-text=\"编写卡片有助于阅读理解\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678936570\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"9\">[9]</sup><br/> </li></ul><h2>链接至本文（已汉化）</h2><ul><li data-pid=\"T6estu3q\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678195187\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">阅读理解问题令人不快</a></li><li data-pid=\"7PPPUjg2\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678405361\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">教材的习题集并不善于检测阅读理解问题</a></li><li data-pid=\"wK8-q8RJ\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/678936570\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\">编写卡片有助于阅读理解</a></li></ul><h2>声明</h2><p data-pid=\"a1kSLiu9\">此内容发布由 Andy Matuschak 许可。未经允许，不得转载或修改。保留所有权利。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"7Sa7nG10\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 GPT-4，校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//notes.andymatuschak.org/zMybAxZcdkJHKSATuSZbEhz\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Reading comprehension (andymatuschak.org)</a></blockquote>",
